---
title: Tandoori Spiced Eggplant with Roasted Veggies, Cilantro Rice and Nigella Seeds
description: Searing the eggplant halves before roasting adds a very unique smoky flavour! Paired with more roasted veggies and cilantro rice, this tandoori spiced dish is delightful!
